OL,7,FIn a version of his speech to the
OL,8,FRoyal United Services Institute (Rusi)
OL,9,Fthinktank, published on the gov.uk
OL,10,Fwebsite, Lord Hermer suggested the
OL,11,FGovernment's approach is a "rejection
OL,12,Fof the siren song" that can be "heard
OL,13,Fin the Palace of Westminster" in which
OL,14,F"Britain abandons the constraints of
OL,15,Finternational law in favour of raw
OL,16,Fpower".
OL,18,F"This is not a new song," he said.
