OL,7,FLord Hermer also said that because of
OL,8,Fwhat happened "in 1933, far-sighted
OL,9,Findividuals rebuilt and transformed
OL,10,Fthe institutions of international
OL,11,Flaw". That is the year that Adolf
OL,12,FHitler became German chancellor.
OL,14,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch has
OL,15,Fstopped short of calling for the UK to
OL,16,Fleave the European Convention on Human
OL,17,FRights (ECHR), as other Conservative
OL,18,Ffigures have advocated.
