OL,7,FHowever, she suggested the UK would
OL,8,Fhave to leave the convention if it
OL,9,Fstops the country from doing "what is
OL,10,Fright".
OL,12,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage has said
OL,13,Fhe would get rid of the ECHR, and told
OL,14,FITV in April that "we have to get back
OL,15,Fthe ability to decide, can we really
OL,16,Fcontrol our borders".
