OL,7,FIn his same speech to Rusi on
OL,8,FThursday, the Attorney General said
OL,9,F"we must not stagnate in our approach
OL,10,Fto international rules" and that
OL,11,Fofficials should "look to apply and
OL,12,Fadapt existing obligations to address
OL,13,Fnew situations".
OL,15,F"We must be ready to reform where
OL,16,Fnecessary," he added.
